Metric: Revenue by Market
Description: Paid revenue + unique customers per market, joining raw_transactions with raw_markets.
Owner: pipeline-builder
Tags: revenue, market, ontology

Source: mart_revenue_by_market

Given the transactions have status "paid"
  And we group by market_id

When we calculate
  Then sum the amount column per market
  And count distinct customers per market

The result is "Revenue by Market"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 24 hours
  Null rate on market_id must be 0%
  Row count must not drop more than 30% day over day
  Value must be between 0 and 10000000
  Duplicate rate on market_id must be 0%
